metadata.name: O.S.S.I. - German
metadata.description:
Mankind as we know it has extinct. New live has evolved and is reviving the earth and the universe.

This story collection will continue to grow.  
By purchasing a token you get full rights to the story and graphics. You can do with it whatever you want.  
Be it commercial use, be it in a book or on websites. All characters can be used for new fanfiction or the likes.

Part 1: O.S.S.I.  
It's the year 2134, mankind has been wiped out/extinguished almost completely. What led to this and who tells the story about the last of the human kind?  
You can find out after purchasing part one.
